Beginner Life and Death Problem.
\b Black to play and live.

\b0 There is a famous vital point in the corner.
It is the \cf1\b 1-2 point\cf0\b0 . However there are two 1-2 point.

One of the 1-2 points usually solves any life and death problem which appears in the corner in 90% of the cases.

Where is the vital point for living in this case?\lang1033\kerning2
